
## 🔍 Project Overview
This project provides an end-to-end **loan portfolio analysis** for a bank to assess credit risk, identify trends, and make **data-driven lending decisions**.

The project covers:
- 📈 **Credit Risk Assessment** – Identify risky borrowers and geographic concentrations.  
- 🧮 **KPI Calculations** – LTV, DTI, Profit/Loss, and more.  
- 🖥️ **Interactive Excel Dashboard** – Dynamic visual insights for decision-makers.  
- 🔮 **Scenario & Sensitivity Analysis** – Model different economic conditions.  

> **Goal:** Improve portfolio health, increase profitability, and reduce default rates.

---

